<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/674976-i-m-enjoying-this-book-but-i-m-wondering">I&#39;m enjoying this book but I&#39;m wondering how much of it is real history and how much is &quot;novel&quot;?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_674976'><a id="like_count_community_question_674976" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/674976?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18765.I_Claudius">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/674976-i-m-enjoying-this-book-but-i-m-wondering">5 years ago</a>
