<a href="/questions/241678-what-is-the-abstract-of-the-novel">what is the abstract of the novel?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_241678'><a id="like_count_community_question_241678" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/241678?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18765.I_Claudius">like</a></span>

