        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1510855" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer131508814654983243">Absolutely one of the worst books I ever read. I will never understand its popularity. Historical fiction at its worst. No themes, no depth, no undertones. Graves simply regurgitates facts and characters from 1st Century Roman high society. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


